                                      Contract Type Performance

                                  BUSINESS QUESTION
Can you break down our customers by contract type, including total customers, total revenue, and average monthly charge??

                                  QUERIES
SELECT
	Contract,
	COUNT(*) total_number_ofcustomers,
	ROUND(SUM(Total_Revenue),2) Total_Revenue,
	AVG(Monthly_Charge) Avg_monthly_charge
FROM telecom_customer
GROUP BY Contract

                                        KEY FINDING
This shows that we have more customers in Month-to-Month Contract than in our One Year Contract and Two Years Contract, and these customers are likely to leave.
They are not fully committed

                                RECOMMENDATIONS
Since most of customers are on Month-to-Month contracts, this suggests a higher risk of churn(thats these customers are most likey to leave )  due to low commitment.
The business can improve retention by encouraging these month-to month  customers to move to One-Year or Two-Year plans through targeted offers, discounts, or 
added value services.
